OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772309090
OL,3,CTeenager sentenced to 11 years for
OL,4,Cmurdering 14-year-old Ibrahima Seck
OL,6,FA 14-year-old boy will be detained for
OL,7,F11 years and 10 months in a young
OL,8,Foffender institution for murdering a
OL,9,Fteenager who was on his way to play
OL,10,Ffootball with friends.
OL,12,FIbrahima Seck, 14, was stabbed in the
OL,13,Fheart on 8 June 2025 in Moston, North
OL,14,FManchester, after a chance encounter
OL,15,Fwith the three teenagers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
