PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772309090
OL,3,CTeenager sentenced to 11 years for
OL,4,Cmurdering 14-year-old Ibrahima Seck
OL,6,FTwo other boys, who cannot be named
OL,7,Ffor legal reasons, were sentenced for
OL,8,Fhis manslaughter, 17-year-old boy will
OL,9,Fbe detained for two years and 10
OL,10,Fmonths, while and a 14-year-old boy
OL,11,Fwill be detained for two years and
OL,12,Ffour months.
OL,14,FThe three teenagers had a chance
OL,15,Fencounter with Ibrahima, his brothers,
OL,16,Fand friends.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
