PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772309090
OL,3,CTeenager sentenced to 11 years for
OL,4,Cmurdering 14-year-old Ibrahima Seck
OL,6,FThey approached Ibrahima's group and,
OL,7,Ffollowing an altercation, the teenager
OL,8,Fwho would go on to stab Ibrahima asked
OL,9,Fthe older boy for the knife, which was
OL,10,Fhanded over.
OL,12,FIbrahima was chased into the Fairways
OL,13,FInn Pub car park, where one of the
OL,14,F14yearolds fatally stabbed him. All
OL,15,Fthree aggressors then fled the scene.
OL,17,FOne of the boys made a video, later
OL,18,Frecovered by the police, where he
OL,19,Fboasted "we just done a murder".
OL,26,@{D@IOU{D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772309090
OL,3,CTeenager sentenced to 11 years for
OL,4,Cmurdering 14-year-old Ibrahima Seck
OL,6,FIbrahima suffered significant injuries
OL,7,Fbut managed to reach a nearby house on
OL,8,FNevin Road to ask for help, where he
OL,9,Fnamed his attacker to those who tried
OL,10,Fto assist him.
OL,12,FResidents administered first aid until
OL,13,Fparamedics arrived, but Ibrahima died
OL,14,Fin hospital a short time later.
OL,16,FA postmortem confirmed the cause of
OL,17,Fdeath was the wound to the heart which
OL,18,Fpenetrated the full thickness of the
OL,19,Ffront of the heart and led to the
OL,20,Fcardiac arrest.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
