FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772309090
OL,3,CTeenager sentenced to 11 years for
OL,4,Cmurdering 14-year-old Ibrahima Seck
OL,6,FIbrahima's father, Mamadou Seck and
OL,7,Ffamily, said after the sentences:
OL,8,F"Ibrahima was a very nice boy. He was
OL,9,Fnot at all a bad person.
OL,11,F"Every person in the world would like
OL,12,FIbrahima if they met him. He was
OL,13,Fsmiling all the time, always wanting
OL,14,Fto help. He is an innocent person. Why
OL,15,FIbrahima?
OL,17,F"He was funny, caring, and hard-
OL,18,Fworking. He was our best friend, and
OL,19,Fhe looked after me.
OL,26,@pD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772309090
OL,3,CTeenager sentenced to 11 years for
OL,4,Cmurdering 14-year-old Ibrahima Seck
OL,6,F"He was so smiley and always made
OL,7,Feverybody laugh. He was a good boy.
OL,8,FThey have not only killed Ibrahima but
OL,9,Fthe whole family and all those people
OL,10,Fwho loved him. Why would anyone do
OL,11,Fthis to him? He did nothing wrong."
OL,13,FMr Seck, originally from Senegal in
OL,14,FWest Africa, said Ibrahima and his
OL,15,Ftwin brothers, 15, were born in
OL,16,FBelgium before the family moved to the
OL,17,FUK in 2018.
OL,19,FHe said Ibrahima, a pupil at Greater
OL,20,FManchester Independent School, was a
OL,21,Fkeen boxer and footballer.
OL,26,@sD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772309090
OL,3,CTeenager sentenced to 11 years for
OL,4,Cmurdering 14-year-old Ibrahima Seck
OL,6,FSpeaking after the sentencing at
OL,7,FManchester Crown Court, Detective
OL,8,FChief Inspector Tony Platten said:
OL,9,F"Today marks the end of a long and
OL,10,Fdifficult trial for the Seck family,
OL,11,Fwhose loving son, Ibrahima Seck, had
OL,12,Fhis life taken from him in a senseless
OL,13,Fact of violence.
OL,15,F"His life was taken suddenly and
OL,16,Fviolently, leaving the Seck family
OL,17,Fwith unimaginable grief: parents
OL,18,Fwithout their son, siblings without a
OL,19,Fbrother, and friends without someone
OL,20,Fthey deeply loved.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772309090
OL,3,CTeenager sentenced to 11 years for
OL,4,Cmurdering 14-year-old Ibrahima Seck
OL,6,F"The impact on those who knew him is
OL,7,Fpermanent and profound.
OL,9,F"Those responsible for this terrible
OL,10,Fcrime, will now serve their sentences
OL,11,Fin prison. But the consequences extend
OL,12,Ffar beyond their time behind bars.
OL,13,FTheir decision to carry and use a
OL,14,Fknife on that day, is something they
OL,15,Fwill carry with them for the rest of
OL,16,Ftheir lives.
OL,18,F"The loss of Ibrahima has affected the
OL,19,Fwhole community surrounding the Moston
OL,20,Farea."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772309090
OL,3,CTeenager sentenced to 11 years for
OL,4,Cmurdering 14-year-old Ibrahima Seck
OL,6,FDCI Platten added: "Choosing not to
OL,7,Fcarry a knife is one of the bravest
OL,8,Fand most important decisions a young
OL,9,Fperson can make.
OL,11,F"It protects you, your friends, your
OL,12,Ffamily and your future. Because once a
OL,13,Fknife is picked up and used, nobody
OL,14,Fwins, and nothing can ever undo the
OL,15,Fdamage it causes.
OL,17,F"This sentence will never take away
OL,18,Fthe pain of losing Ibrahima. Their
OL,19,Floss is permanent, their grief is
OL,20,Flifelong, and no sentence can undo
OL,21,Fwhat happened to their son.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
