PN,39610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772309090
OL,3,CTeenager sentenced to 11 years for
OL,4,Cmurdering 14-year-old Ibrahima Seck
OL,6,F"I urge anyone who has even the
OL,7,Fslightest suspicion that someone they
OL,8,Fknow is carrying a knife to speak to
OL,9,Fthem, challenge them, and report it to
OL,10,Fpolice.
OL,12,F"If you don't feel comfortable
OL,13,Fspeaking to police, you can report
OL,14,Fthis information to Fearless, an
OL,15,Foffshoot of charity Crimestoppers,
OL,16,Faimed at providing young people a safe
OL,17,Fspace to report crime anonymously."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@cO]
